data.description: Move in ready pool home for sale in Edgewater, FL. This home has been well taken care of by the current owners and has a brand new HVAC system, 5 year old roof, & new updated vinyl flooring. The home sits on a double corner lot that is higher than most in the area & the outside is already fenced with a large covered porch for entertaining friends and family! Conveniently located 5 minutes from shopping, the river, and about 15 minutes from New Smyrna Beach!
